This pull request exposes shape components prop types, so it will be easier to wrap the original components into custom components. Currently, our team uses the next workaround to inherit the original component props: 

```typescript
import { BarRounded } from '@visx/shape';

type StyledBar = Omit<Parameters<typeof BarRounded>[0], 'ref'> & {
  // ...our custom props
}
```

While it works well for plain components, things get more complicated when it comes to generic components (like `LinePath`). So, it would be useful to expose the original types from the library itself. 

#### :rocket: Enhancements

- expose shape components prop types

